Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,梦传递着来自深处的讯息\NDreams are messages from the deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的星球  厄拉科斯  在日落时分尤为美丽\NMy planet, Arrakis, is so beautiful when the sun is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,尘沙翻滚...\NRolling over the sands…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以看到空气中都弥漫着香料\NYou can see spice in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,旁晚时分  香料收割机登陆\NAt nightfall, the spice harvesters land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,外来者争分夺秒的收割  因为他们要躲避炽热的白天\NThe outsiders race against time to avoid the heat of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在我们眼前蹂躏我们的土地\NThey ravage our lands in front of our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知  他们对我们的人民异常残忍\NTheir cruelty to my people is all I've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这些外来者  哈科宁人  早在我出生之前就来了\NThese outsiders, The Harkonnens, came long before I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,通过控制香料生产  他们变得非常富有\NBy controlling the spice production they became obscenely rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至比皇帝还富有\NRicher than the Emperor himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的战士也无法将厄拉科斯从哈科宁人手中解救出来\NOur warriors couldn't free Arrakis from the Harkonnens,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有一天  皇帝颁布法令  哈科宁人消失了\Nbut one day, by imperial decree, they were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝为什么要这么做  我们的下一个压迫者又会是谁呢\NWhy did the Emperor choose this path? And who our next oppressors be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:03.48,Default,tx,0,0,0,,沙  丘  瀚  战\N\N上 部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,公元10191年\NYEAR 10191
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉丹  阿特雷季斯家族故土\NCALADAN HOMEWORLD OF HOUSE ATREIDES
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你起这么早  不错\NIt's good you're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲命你在皇帝的使者到来之前穿上正装\NFather wants you in full dress before the Emperor's herald arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,正装  还是军装\NFull dress? Military?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,礼服\NCeremonial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,既然已经决定了  为什么还要经历这一切呢\NWhy do we have to go through all of this when it's already been decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,仪式需要\NCeremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要水  就叫我给你\NIf you want it make me give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-用密语说  -妈妈 我才刚睡醒\N-Use the Voice. -Mom, I just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-把水给我  -这声音连玻璃都听不见 你得命令我\N-Give me the water. -The glass can't hear you. Command me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把水给我\NGive me the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-差不多了  -差不多了?\N-Almost. -Almost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尼·格瑟里特的密语技能需要很多年才能学会  保罗\NBene Gesserit skills take years to learn, Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很疲惫  做了很多梦吗\NYou look tired. More dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,极端温度和变化无常的天气\NExtreme temperatures and treacherous weather events
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让厄拉科斯城外的生活条件变得异常恶劣\Nmake life outside the cities of Arrakis truly hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沙尘暴的威力足以穿透金属\NWith sandstorms powerful enough to cut through the metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只有被称为弗里曼人的土著部落能够适应这种条件  从而生存下来\NOnly the native tribes known as the Fremen have adapted well enough to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们更喜欢居住在厄拉科斯最偏远的地区\NPreferring to inhabit the remotest regions of Arrakis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里曼人与巨大的沙虫居住在沙漠深处\Nthe Fremen share the deep desert with the giant sandworms
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里曼人将沙虫称为沙胡鲁德\Nknown to the Fremen as Shai-Hulud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,长期接触香料给他们部落带来了特有的蓝色眼睛\NLong exposure to spice has given the tribe their characteristic blue eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,伊巴德之眼\Nthe eyes of Ibad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人对弗里曼人知之甚少\NLittle else is known of the Fremen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只知道他们异常危险  而且很不可靠\Nexcept that they are dangerous and unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,由于弗里曼人的侵袭  收割香料变得困难重重\NFremen attacks make spice harvesting extremely hazardous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对弗里曼人来说  香料是神圣的迷幻剂\NFor the Fremen, spice is the sacred hallucinogen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅能维持生命  还很有益于身体健康\Nwhich preserves life and brings enormous health benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对于帝国而言  香料则能帮助太空行会的领航员们\NFor the Imperium, the spice is used by the navigators of the Spacing Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,找到星球之间的安全路径\Nto find safe paths between the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有香料  就无法进行星际旅行\NWithout spice interstellar travel is impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这也使得香料成为了字宙中最有价值的物质\Nmaking it by far the most valuable substance in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,注意微笑  格尼\NSmile, Gurney.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在微笑呢\NI am smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们大老远跑来参加这个仪式  要花多少钱\NHow much will it cost them traveling all this way for this formality?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,三名行会领航员需要花费1460062索拉里斯币用于往返旅行\NThree Guild navigators and a total of 1,460,062 solaris for the round trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙皇帝沙达姆·科里诺四世\NBy the grace of Shaddam IV of the House Corrino,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,登上已知宇宙帕迪沙皇帝的金狮宝座的恩典\NAscendant to the Golden Lion Throne of Padishah Emperor of the Known Universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我作为变革的先驱站在你们面前\NI stand before you as Herald of the Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在此将得到朝廷成员\NWe are witnessed by members of the Imperial Court,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太空协会代表  以及贝内·格表里特女先知的见证\Nrepresentatives of the Spacing Guild, and a sister of the Bene Gesserit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝有旨\NThe Emperor has spoken:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"厄崔迪家族应立即接管厄拉科斯\N"House Atreides shall immediately take control of Arrakis
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,并掌管此地"\Nand serve as its steward."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你领旨吗\NDo you accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是厄崔迪家族\NWe are the House Atreides.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝不抗旨  我们绝不弃信\NThere is no call we do not answer. There is no faith that we betray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝要求我们给厄拉科斯带来和平\NThe Emperor asks us to bring peace to Arrakis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,厄崔迪家族必不辱使命\NHouse Atreides accepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,厄崔迪\NAtreides!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,盖下你的印戒\NYour seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  就这些流程吗\NSo, it's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些\NIt's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -稳定器太松了\N-How was it? -The stabilizers are too loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-我来处理  -谢谢你 我的朋友\N-I'll handle that. -Thank you, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-邓肯  -好小子\N-Duncan. -My boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗  我的好小子\NPaul, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  你明天要和先遣部队一起去厄拉科斯吗\NSo, you're going to Arrakis tomorrow with the advance team?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我明天要和先遣部队一起去厄拉科斯\NYes, I'm going to Arrakis tomorrow with the advance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-我想让你带我一起去  -你想去吗\N-I'd like you to take me with you. -You would?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那可惨了  因为你不能去\NThat's too bad, cause no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,邓肯\NDuncan…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想把我送上军事法庭吗  到底怎么回事啊\NAre you trying to give me court-martial? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我能信任你吗  -绝对可以 你知道的\N-Can I trust you with something? -Always. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在做梦\NI've been having dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,关于厄拉科斯和弗里曼人\NAbout Arrakis and the Fremen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  所以呢\NOkay, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你了\NI saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和弗里曼人在一起\NWith the Fremen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我真的找到他们了吗  那是好兆头啊\NSo I do find them? There you go. That's a good omen right there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,兰维尔\NLanville!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你躺在床上死了  司在战斗中阵亡了\NI saw you lying dead. Fallen in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得如果我去那里的话  你可能能活下来\NI felt like if I had been there you'd be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  我不会死的\NFirst of, I'm not gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-你根本没把我的话当回事  -这就是你想和我一起去的原因吗\N-You're not taking me seriously. -That's why you wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  梦里面什么都有\NListen, dreams make good stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有我们醒着的时候  发生的一切才尤为重要\Nbut everything important happens when we're awake,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为醒着的才是真实的\Nbecause that's where we make things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-看看你 长了不少肌肉了呀  -有吗\N-Look at you, put up some muscle? -I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等到了厄拉科斯再见  小子\NSee you in Arrakis, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲  父亲我想申请跟邓肯·爱达荷一起\NFather, I'd like to ask to join Duncan Idaho
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,明天去厄拉科斯执行侦察任务\Non a scout mission to Arrakis tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我学过弗里曼语  能派得上用场\NI've studied the Fremen language. I'd be an asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想都别想\NOut of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须等几周后才能跟我们剩下的人过去\NYou'll travel in a few weeks to Arrakis like the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生都在训练... 如果派不上用场\NI've been training my whole life… What is the point if I'm not allowed--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道原因的  保罗  你是厄崔迪家族的未来\NYou know why, Paul. You're the future of the House Atreides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,祖父曾为了朋友而与公牛搏斗\NAnd grandfather fought bulls for sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  看看他的下场\NYes, look where that got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你在我身边\NI need you by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们到达厄拉科斯时  我们会面临巨大的危险\NWhen we get to Arrakis we'll face enormous danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什么危险  是弗里曼人  还是沙漠\NWhat danger? The Fremen? The desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,政治风险\NPolitical danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们领导着的大家族  威胁到了皇帝\NThe great houses look to us for leadership and this threatens the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把厄拉科斯从哈科宁家族手中夺走  把它变成了我们的\NBy taking Arrakis from the Harkonnens and making it ours
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝是在酝酿一场削弱两大家族的战争\Nhe sets the stage for a war which would weaken both houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们坚定不移地挖掘出厄拉科斯的真正力量\NBut if we hold firm and tap the true power of Arrakis
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以比以往任何时候都更强大\Nwe could be stronger than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,开采香料  弗里曼会无动于衷吗\NMining spice, keeping the Fremen in their place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会比哈科宁家族好到哪里去\NWe'd be no better than Harkonnens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我们是要与弗里曼人结盟\NNo. By making an alliance with the Fremen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我派邓肯·爱达荷就是去安排这件事\NThat's what I've sent Duncan Idaho to arrange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里  在卡拉丹  我们培养了空中力量和海上力量\NHere, on Caladan, we've ruled by air power and sea power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在厄拉科斯  我们需要培养沙漠力量\NOn Arrakis, we need to cultivate desert power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你参加我的会议  了解我的工作\NI want you sitting in on my council, learn what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不想呢  爸爸\NWhat if I'm not, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不想做什么\NNot what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想当厄崔迪家族的未来\NThe future of the House Atreides.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也曾告诉我父亲我也不想这样\NI told my father I didn't want this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-我曾经梦想成为一名飞行员  -你从来没跟我讲过\N-I wanted to be a pilot. -You never told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你祖父说过  伟大的人不会想成为领导\NYour grandfather said, "A great man doesn't seek to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但一经召唤  必带头冲锋\NHe's called to it. And he answers."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想\NAnd if your answer is "no"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是我唯一需要的人\Nyou'll still be the only thing I ever needed you to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\Nmy son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己做好了自己的选择  也许你也会\NI found my own way to it. Maybe you'll find yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一片回忆里...\NIn their memory…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你也试试看\Ngive it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要背对着门站着\NDon't stand with your back to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要告诉你多少次\NHow many times do we have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我从脚步声就知道是你  格尼·哈莱克\NI could tell it was you by your footsteps, Gurney Halleck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,万一别人模仿我的脚步声呢\NSomeone might imitate my stride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我能分辨出来  你现在是新的武器大师了吗\NI know the difference. Are you the new weapons master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,邓肯·爱达荷离开了  我必须尽我所能\NWith Duncan Idaho gone, I must make do as best as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,选一把你的刀吧\NChoose your blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,格尼  我今天过得挺不错的  不如我们来唱首歌吧\NI've had quite a day, Gurney. Give us a song instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真粗鲁\NThat's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  来吧\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老头\NOld man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这么慢的速度都能击穿你的屏蔽场\NThe slow blade penetrates the shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-我猜我今天没心情  -心情 这跟心情有什么关系\N-I'm guessing I'm not in the mood today. -Mood? What's mood got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,战争可不会管你心情好不好  赶紧  来战斗\NYou fight when the necessity arises, no matter the mood. Now, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-我打败你了  -没错\N-I have you. -Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是请看你下面  你会和我一起死的\NBut look down, my lord. You'd have joined me in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你现在心情不错了\NI see you found the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-情况真的很糟吗  -你还不明白吗\N-Will it be that bad? -You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你没有真正了解  发生在我们身上的事情到底有多严重\NYou don't really understand the grave nature of what's happening to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,80年来  厄拉科斯一直属于哈科宁家族\NFor 80 years Arrakis belonged to House Harkonnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们管理香料国八十年了  你能想象他们有多富有吗\NEighty years of owning the spice fields. Can you imagine the wealth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的眼睛里  我没有看到该有的眼神\NIn your eyes, I need to see it in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前从没见过哈科宁人  我见过\NYou never met Harkonners before. I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是人  禽兽不如\NThey are not human. They're brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须做好准备\NYou have to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吉迪主星  哈科宁家族故土\NGIEDI PRIME HOMEWORLD OF HOUSE HARKONNEN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,男爵大人\NLord Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拉班\NRabban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后一艘飞船已经离开了厄拉科斯  已经全部完成\NThe last of our ships have left Arrakis. It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好\NVery good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔  我们怎么能容忍这种事\NUncle, how did we let this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝怎么能夺走我们所打造的一切\NHow can the Emperor take everything we've built
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拱手送给那个公爵  怎么能这样\Nand give it to that Duke? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样  这是爱\NDon't be too sure, it's an act of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\NWhat does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,塞翁失马焉知非福\NWhen is a gift not a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,厄崔迪家族声名鹊起\NThe Atreides Voice is rising
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝是个善妒的人\Nand the Emperor is a jealous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,危险  善妒\NA dangerous, jealous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗...\NPaul…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗  醒醒\NPaul, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -穿上衣服跟我来\N-What's wrong? -Get dressed and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尊敬的盖尤斯·海伦·莫希亚姆女先知在这里\NThe Reverend Mother Gaius Helen Mohiam is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我在贝内格塞里特学院的老师\NShe was my teacher at the Bene Gesserit school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在是皇帝的先知\NShe's now Truthsayer to the Emperor himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她想见见你\NShe would like to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她想听听你的梦\NShe wants to know about your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么知道我的梦的\NHow does she know about my dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-岳医生怎么会在这里  -他只需要耽搁你一小会儿\N-And why is Dr. Yueh here? -He only needs a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  少爷\NHello, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈让我检查一下你的生命体征\NYour mother asked me to check your vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了呢\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:06.20,Default,tag,0,0,35,,贝内格赛里特的事儿  我是略有所闻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.76,Default,tag,0,0,35,,他们说他们的存在  是为了要造福更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:12.88,Default,tag,0,0,35,,我并不是要冒犯你母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:16.20,Default,tag,0,0,35,,但说到底  他们所做的一切  都是为了他们自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当心点\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他的心脏一如既往的健康  夫人\NHis heart is strong as ever, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对任何人都不能说这件事\NNot a word of this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗\NPaul…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,记住你训练的那些\NRemember your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛里带着挑衅的神情  就像他父亲一样\NDefiance in the eyes, like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你出去吧\NLeave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须照海伦·莫希亚姆先知告诉你的去做\NYou must do everything the Mother Helen Mohiam tells you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我妈妈赶出了她自己的房子\NYou dismiss my mother in her own house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,到这儿来  跪下\NCome here. Kneel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么敢对我使用密语\NHow dare you use the Voice on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的右手放进盒子里\NPut your right hand in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲吩咐你得服从我的命令\NYour mother bade you obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:24:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需在你的脖子上扎一根戈姆·贾巴尔的毒针  你立马毙命\NI hold at your neck the Gom Jabbar, a poison needle, instant death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个测试很简单\NThe test is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你把手从盒子里拿开  你就必死无疑\NRemove your hand from the box, and you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这盒子里是什么\NWhat's in the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦\NPain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要叫警卫\NNo need to call the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈就在那扇门后面  没有她的吩附  谁也进不来\NYour mother stands behind that door. No one will get past her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.24,0:24:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,落入陷阱的动物会咬断自己的腿逃跑\NAn animal caught in a trap will gnaw off its own leg to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.32,0:24:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你会怎么做\NWhat will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.32,0:25:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,安静\NSilence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能害怕\NI must not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.01,0:25:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能害怕\NI must not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.44,0:25:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,恐惧是心灵杀手\NFear is the mind-killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.60,0:25:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,恐惧会带来毁灭\NFear is the little death that brings obliteration.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.16,0:25:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我得直面我的恐惧  当恐惧来袭时\NI will face my fear and I will permit it to pass over me and through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:25:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我得让恐惧随风而逝\NAnd when it has gone past…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我得敞开心扉  看着恐惧来去\NI will turn the inner eye to see its path.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.56,0:26:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,恐惧消失之地  什么也不会留下\NWhere the fear has gone there will be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.52,0:26:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我会留下\NOnly I will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.26,0:26:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\NEnough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就像筛沙子一样  我们只是负责筛人\NLike sifting sand through a screen, we sift people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.68,0:26:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你像动物一样  无法控制自己的冲动\NIf you had been unable to control your impulses like an animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.16,0:26:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就不能让你活下去\Nwe could not have let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.39,0:26:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要继承的权力实在太多\NYou inherit too much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么 因为我是公爵的儿子吗  -因为你是杰西卡的儿子\N-What, because I'm a Duke's son? -Because you are Jessica's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.88,0:27:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你生来就被赋予了太多权力  孩子\NYou have more than one birthright, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.80,0:27:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,杰西卡\NJessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.72,0:27:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,某种程度上来说  你一直在训练他\NYou've been training him in a Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.16,0:27:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-给我讲讲这些梦吧  -我今晚就做了个梦\N-Tell me about these dreams. -I had one tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.12,0:27:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,梦到了什么\NWhat did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.76,0:27:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-厄拉科斯的一个女孩  -你以前梦见过她吗\N-A girl on Arrakis. -Have you dreamt of her before?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.96,0:27:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,梦到过很多次了\NMany times.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.92,0:27:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你梦到的事总是变成了现实吗\NDo you often dream things that happen just as you dreamt them?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.48,0:27:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也不全是\NNot exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.80,0:27:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  年轻人  我希望你能活下来\NGoodbye, young human. I hope you'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.52,0:28:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你非得这样做吗\NDid you have to go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.72,0:28:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你无视规则选择用这种方式训练他\NYou chose to train him in the Way in defiance of the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.28,0:28:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他使用了我们的力量  就必须接受最大限度的考验\NHe wields our power. He had to be tested to the limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.76,0:28:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在男人身上浪费了太多的潜力\NSo much potential wasted in the male.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.90,0:28:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来只能生女儿\NYou were told to bear only daughters,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.79,0:28:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你出于自尊  总认为你能生出救世主\Nbut you and your pride thought you could produce the Kwisatz Haderach.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了吗\NWas I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.35,0:28:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该感到幸运  他没有死在那个房间里\NYou're lucky he didn't die in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.42,0:28:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他就是救世主  那他还有很长的路要走\NIf he is The One he has a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.56,0:28:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他的洞察力还未被唤醒  现在却身陷火海\NHis sight is barely awakened and now he goes into the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.72,0:28:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我们的计划是以世纪为单位来计算的\NBut our plans are measured in centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.04,0:28:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他没有成功\NWe have other prospects
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.12,0:28:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有别的希望\Nif he fails his promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.56,0:28:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你所看到的希望真就这么渺茫吗\NDo you see so little hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.92,0:28:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在厄拉科斯  我们已经为你做了我们能做的一切\NOn Arrakis, we have done all we can for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.04,0:28:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,道路已经铺设好了  希望他不要浪费时机\NThe path has been laid. Let's hope he doesn't squander it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.28,0:29:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗\NPaul…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.48,0:29:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\NWhat does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.24,0:29:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-我可以成为救世主?  -你听到了?\N-That I can be The One? -You heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.44,0:29:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,贝内·格塞里特家族跟各大家族都是合作伙伴\NThe Bene Gesserit serve as powerful partners to the great houses,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.11,0:29:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实还有更深层的原因\Nbut there's more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.28,0:29:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你在暗中搅动帝国的政治\NYou stir the politics on the Imperium from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.32,0:30:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道  -你并不知道全情\N-I know. -You don't know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.39,0:30:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,万载千秋\NFor thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.90,0:30:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在小心翼翼地跨越血统  就是为了诞生...\Nwe've been carefully crossing bloodlines to bring forth--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.44,0:30:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主吗\NThe One?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.16,0:30:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一个...\NA mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.80,0:30:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,强大到足以突破空间和时间  过去和未来的...\Npowerful enough to breach space and time, past and future…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.48,0:30:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮助我们走向更美好的未来的人\Nwho can help us into a better future.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.76,0:30:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为已经快找到他了\NWe think he's very close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.28,0:30:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人觉得他就在这里\NSome believe he is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是你们计划的一部分\NAll part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.64,0:32:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,开启屏蔽场\NShields.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.60,0:33:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"我的肺吸入了时间的气息  吹过了飘落的沙子"\N"My lungs taste the air of Time, Blown past falling sands."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.32,0:34:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲尔·哈瓦特\NThufir Hawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.84,0:34:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷  新世界感觉如何\NYoung master, how does it feel to walk on the new world?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.72,0:34:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,算是挺兴奋的吧\NExciting, to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.28,0:34:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-大人  -你好吗 老朋友\N-My Lord. -How are you, old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.04,0:34:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的先遣部队已经守卫了这座城市\NMy advance team has secured the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.34,0:34:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在清理一些不顺的地方\NWe're still smoothing out a few rough spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.32,0:34:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人\NMy Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.00,0:34:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,(异域先知)\NLisan al-Gaib!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.20,0:35:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(异域先知)\NLisan al-Gaib!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.72,0:35:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别被他们的欢迎愚弄了\NDon't be fooled by the welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.60,0:35:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是遵循他们的老主人的规则  强制侍从\NThey follow their old master's rules, mandatory attendancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.55,0:35:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁人喜欢在外面搞这些玩意儿\NThat's Harkonnen love out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.36,0:35:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,厄崔迪\NAtreides!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.18,0:35:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你们离开这吧\NLet's get you out of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.83,0:35:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方热得要命\NThe heat can kill in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.85,0:36:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们喊的是我们\NThey were pointing at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.26,0:36:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在喊什么\NWhat were they shouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.91,0:36:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisan al-Gaib 意思是异域先知\NLisan al-Gaib. "The Voice from the Outer World."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.60,0:36:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他们对 "救世主" 的称呼\NIt's their name for "messiah."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.53,0:36:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着贝内格瑟里特家族在这里做了些事\NThat means that Bene Gesserit have done a work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.68,0:36:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,散布迷信吗\NPlanting superstitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.12,0:36:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫开辟道路  保罗\NPreparing the way, Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.88,0:36:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人已经等了几个世纪的救世主\NThese people have waited for centuries for the Lisan al-Gaib.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.32,0:36:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看到你  看到了征兆\NThey see you, they see the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.72,0:36:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看到的不过是道听途说的而已\NThey see what they've been told to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.28,0:36:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以走了\NWe're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.40,0:37:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,屏蔽墙  能保护城市免受天气和沙虫的侵袭\NShield wall, protects the city from the weather and the worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.20,0:38:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,当地人称之为 "上帝之手"\NThe locals call the big one the "Hand of God."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.48,0:38:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝之手正在破坏我们的通讯系统\NWell, the Hand of God is wreaking havoc on our com system.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.48,0:38:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好安静啊\NIt's so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.08,0:38:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  这也是我所担心的\NYeah. That's what worries me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.32,0:38:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一个太空港\NThere's a space port,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.23,0:38:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在那厚厚的灰尘里有一家香料精炼厂\Nand in that plump of dust there's a spice refinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.68,0:38:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最薄弱的两个地方  我要你看好\NOur two most vulnerable points. I want you guarding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.16,0:38:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不能提炼香料运出去  我们就完蛋了\NIf we can't refine spice and ship it off to the world, we're dead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.12,0:38:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳升起来了  我们得把门封起来\NThe sun is getting too high. We need to seal the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.08,0:39:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么形容这的\NWhat do they say about this hell hole again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.32,0:39:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"纯天然沐浴  你能用沙子洗澡"\N"It's a shower, you scrub your ass with sand,"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.39,0:39:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大人  他们是这么说的\NMy Lord, that's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.04,0:39:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么说的啊\NThat's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.92,0:39:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是管家候选人  夫人\NCandidates for a house keeper, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.84,0:39:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-你叫什么名字  -沙多特·麦普斯 夫人\N-What is your name? -Shadout Mapes, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.92,0:39:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们剩下的可以走了  谢谢\NThe rest of you may go. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.12,0:39:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沙多特\NShadout.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.84,0:39:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一古老的脉轮单词\NIt's an old chakobsa word.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.72,0:39:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是 "优秀的浸染工"\N"Well dipper."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.27,0:39:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你是弗里曼人\NYou are Fremen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.36,0:39:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-你很精通古语吗  -我精通很多东西\N-You know the ancient tongues? -I know many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我还知道你们体内藏着武器\NI know that you have a weapon concealed in your bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.96,0:39:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.52,0:40:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想伤害我  我必须警告你  不管你体内藏着什么武器\NIf you mean to harm me, I must warn you whatever you're hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.64,0:40:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不够使的\Nit won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.08,0:40:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的武器是一件礼物\NMy weapon is meant as a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.16,0:40:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真的是救世主\Nif you are truly The One.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.40,0:40:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个吗\NDo you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.00,0:40:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一把晶牙匕\NIt's a crysknife.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.12,0:40:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这意味着什么吗\NDo you know its meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,做好准备\NBe ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.56,0:40:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,意味着造物者\NIt's a maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.52,0:40:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来自沙漠深处的造物者\NA maker of the deep desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.44,0:40:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当你带着一个预言生活了这么久\NWhen you have lived with a prophecy for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.77,0:40:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等到启示之时一定深感震惊吧\Nthe moment of revelation is a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.96,0:41:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,异域先知  母与子\NLisan al-Gaib. The mother and the son.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.68,0:41:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这归你了\NIt is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.92,0:41:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沙虫之齿\NTooth of Shai-Hulud.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.44,0:41:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.08,0:42:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这么热你不该来这里\NYou shouldn't be out here at this time of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.60,0:42:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都在外面啊\NThey are out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.48,0:42:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是弗里曼朝圣者  他们不怕中暑\NFremen pilgrims. They don't care about heat stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.32,0:42:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到这里还能找到棕榈树\NI didn't know date palms could even be found out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.40,0:42:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这些可不是自然生长的  没有我它们活不下去\NThese aren't indigenous. They can't survive without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.32,0:42:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,每棵树每天需要的水量相当于五个人\NEach one of these drinks every day the equivalent of five man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.72,0:42:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,二十棵棕榈树  能供一百个人用水\NTwenty palm trees. A hundred lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.08,0:42:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么不砍了这些树 节约用水  -不 不\N-Should we remove them? Save the water? -No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.24,0:42:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这些树是神圣的\NThese are sacred.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.16,0:42:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怀着古老的梦想\NOld dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.16,0:42:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,厄拉科斯上最庞大最危险的有机体是沙虫\NThe largest and the most dangerous organism on Arrakis is the sandworm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.24,0:43:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能够长到400米长\NCapable of reaching 400 meters in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.16,0:43:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为避免发出有带奏的声音引来沙虫\NTo avoid making rhythmic noises which attract the sandworms,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.24,0:43:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里曼人穿越沙漠时\Nthe Fremen cross desert spaces using the sand walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.12,0:43:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会用不规则节奏的舞姿前行\Na dance-like motion with irregular rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.93,0:43:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,模仿沙漠的自然声音\Nwhich emulates the natural sounds of the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.96,0:43:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,厄拉科斯仅存的植物要归功于弗里曼人\NWhat scant plant life exists on Arrakis is thanks to the Fremen,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.24,0:43:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们种植了深根植物\Nwho have cultivated deep-rooted terrain plants,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.11,0:43:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如萨瓜罗 囊泡果\Nsuch as saguaro, burrobush,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.24,0:43:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沙马鞭草和香丛\Nsand verbena and incense bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.08,0:43:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,金树树根最深\NThe shepherd's tree has the deepest documented roots,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.32,0:43:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能伸展超过450英尺深\Nstretching more than 450 feet deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.64,0:43:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这些植物在干燥贫瘠的土地上生存\NThese plants cling to life in a parched nutrient-poor landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.12,0:44:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是猎镖  一定有什么人在附近\NIt's a hunter-seeker. The operator must be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.44,0:45:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁的特工是六周前被塞进那个洞的\NThe Harkonnen agent was cemented into that hole six weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.94,0:45:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,通过墙内的水管操纵猎镖\NManned the hunter-seeker through a water pipe inside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.04,0:45:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我今天让您失望了  都怪我\NSir, I failed you today. There's no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.25,0:45:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你提交辞呈\NYou have my resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.88,0:45:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想让我们失去你这么优秀的人才?  -先生 我的失职让我有辱声誉\N-You'd deprive us of your talents? -Sir, my honor demands--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.96,0:45:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想害我儿子性命\NThey tried to take the life of my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.76,0:45:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你的声誉  你想要赎罪吗  抓几个间谍吧\NI don't give a damn about your honor. You want absolution? Go catch some spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.47,0:45:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命\NYour Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.88,0:45:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让那玩意儿出去\NThe thing must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.16,0:45:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,您尽管说  宠物是听不懂话的\NYou can speak without fear. Our pet doesn't understand your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.96,0:45:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.64,0:45:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它听得懂  保持安静\NIt understands. Activate silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.84,0:45:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝有什么口谕\NWhat is the Emperor's message?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.08,0:45:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他要加强你的力量\NHe will strengthen your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.88,0:45:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让他的萨督卡皇家部队助你一臂之力\NWith his Sardaukar army…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.44,0:46:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能让任何人知道\NIt must never be known.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.96,0:46:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,厄拉科斯上空没有卫星  厄崔迪家族会在黑暗中葬身\NThere's no satellites over Arrakis. The Atreides would die in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.16,0:46:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事\NOn that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.06,0:46:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,莱托·厄崔迪公爵与我们毫无瓜葛\NDuke Leto Atreides means nothing to our order.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.12,0:46:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但他的妻子得受我们保护  因此  她的儿子也得受我们保护\NBut his wife is under our protection, and by extension, her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.20,0:46:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们享有流放该有的尊严\NAllow them the dignity of exile.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.20,0:46:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁家族做梦也不敢违背您的神圣指令\NHouse Harkonnen would never dream of violating the sanctity of your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.68,0:46:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应你  我们不会伤害他们的\NI give you my word. We would not harm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.40,0:46:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-如果公爵的儿子还活着的话  -厄崔迪家族一个也别想活\N-If the Duke's son lives-- -No Atreides will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.00,0:46:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大人  你向女巫保证过  而且她明察秋毫\NMy Lord, you gave your word to the witch. And she sees too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.96,0:47:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过我不会伤害他们  我当然不会伤害\NI said I would not harm them. And I shall not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.96,0:47:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是厄拉科斯毕竟是厄拉科斯\NBut Arrakis is Arrakis,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.48,0:47:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠总是会消灭弱者\Nand the desert takes the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.76,0:47:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的沙漠\NMy desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.84,0:47:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我的厄拉科斯\NMy Arrakis.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.60,0:47:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的沙丘\NMy dune.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.24,0:47:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你第一次战略会议\NYour first strategy meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.58,0:47:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗厄崔迪  他赤手空拳抓到猎镖  堪比所有人的英雄\NPaul Atreides, who catches hunter-seekers in his bare hands like a hero of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.36,0:47:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢你的羞辱 老头  -我会看着你的\N-Thanks for the humiliation, old man. -I'll keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.28,0:47:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,起立\NAttention!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.20,0:47:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧\NLet's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.88,0:47:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲尔  行动组\NThufir, operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.12,0:47:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄到了一份哈科宁家族的账簿\NI've secured a copy of the Harkonnen's account books.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.44,0:48:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁家族每年从这里赚取100亿索拉利斯币\NThe Harkonnens were taking 10 billion solaris out of here every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.56,0:48:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不仅吸食丰富的海产\N"They shall suck at the abundance of the seas
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.81,0:48:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还有藏在沙子里的宝藏\Nand on the treasures hidden in the sand."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.64,0:48:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们暂时无法取得这样的利润\NWe won't see profits like that for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.99,0:48:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有给我们留下设备\Nnot with the equipment they left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.88,0:48:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,情况到底如何\NHow bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.24,0:48:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是香料仓\NThese are spice silos.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.50,0:48:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得装满所有的板条箱\NWe are meant to fill every crate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.60,0:48:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的吗\NAll of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.32,0:48:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,每隔25个标准日就得装满一次\NEvery 25 standard days.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.14,0:48:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁的破坏让我们节奏慢了许多\NHarkonnen sabotage slows us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.56,0:48:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁负责维护呢\NBut who's meant to arbitrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.08,0:48:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有变时裁决官来负责移交吗\NIsn't there a Judge of the Change to oversee the transition?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.56,0:48:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-皇帝任命了谁  -列特·凯恩斯博士 帝国生态学家\N-Who did the Emperor appoint? -Dr. Liet Kynes, imperial ecologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.80,0:48:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里经呆了20年了  据我所知 性情古怪\NBeen here 20 years. Eccentric from what I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.00,0:48:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想亲眼看看那些要收割的田地\NI want to see these harvesting fields myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.81,0:48:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不推荐这样做  大人\NI wouldn't recommend it, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.28,0:48:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让这位变时裁决官陪我们一起去吧\NHave this Judge of the Change accompany us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.14,0:48:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的会议本来已经延误了\NOur meeting is long overdue.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.88,0:48:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要得到一点帝国的保护\NAnd we'll get a bit of imperial protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.86,0:48:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这算人质吗  我喜欢\NA hostage? I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.52,0:48:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了  大人\NHe's here, my lord
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.84,0:49:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾好他们  他们是朋友\NTake care of them, they are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.72,0:49:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-邓肯  -我的好小子\N-Duncan! -My boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.64,0:49:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-你肯定又长高了  -好吧 你闻着更臭了\N-I swear you're getting taller. -Well, you smell much worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.08,0:49:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我和弗里曼人一起住了四周\NFor four weeks I've lived with the Fremen,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.13,0:49:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们躲在沙漠中的一个部落  称之为穴地\Nhidden in the desert, in the community called the sietch.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.60,0:49:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个穴地的领导者  史蒂加  已经和我一起来见你了  先生\NStilgar, the leader of that sietch has come with me to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.64,0:49:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-穴地 他们是怎么躲起来的   -躲在地下\N-This sietch, how was it hidden? -It's under ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.36,0:49:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,厄拉科斯到处都是洞穴\NArrakis is filled with caverns.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.20,0:49:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方有多大\NHow big was the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.08,0:49:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有上万人  而且有几百个穴地\NIt's a ten thousand people, and there are hundreds of sietches.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.72,0:50:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,数百万的弗里曼人  你猜对了\NMillions of Fremen. You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.12,0:50:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,据哈科宁估计  这整个星球上只有5万人\NThe Harkonnen estimate was fifty thousand on the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.96,0:50:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里曼人看着我找了好几天  我一直没找到\NThe Fremen watched me search for them for days. I never saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.44,0:50:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,最后  他们派了一个勇士来杀我\NFinally, they sent a warrior out to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.40,0:50:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我得说  我从未如此接近死亡\Nand I have to tell you, I've never come so close to dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.47,0:50:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,帝国没有比他更厉害的战士了\NThere's no finer fighter in the Imperium.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.56,0:50:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们像恶魔一样战斗  -这就是沙漠力量\N-They fight like demons. -Desert power.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.60,0:50:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-邓肯 干得好  -谢谢您 大人\N-Duncan, well done. -Thank you, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.04,0:50:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  他们的首领有一把刀  他不愿意缴械  长官\NSir, their leader has a knife he won't surrender, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.96,0:50:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那是晶牙匕  对他们来说非常神圣\NIt's a crysknife, it's sacred to his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.72,0:50:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,让他进来吧\NLet him pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.77,0:50:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,站住别动\NStop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.37,0:50:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  嘿\NHey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.16,0:51:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂加  欢迎你\NStilgar, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.80,0:51:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我很尊重那些愿意尊重我的人\NSir, I respect the personal dignity of any man that respects mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.83,0:51:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\NHold.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.68,0:51:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  史蒂加  谢谢来自你体液的厚礼\NThank you, Stilgar, for the gift of your body's moisture.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.96,0:51:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会接受你的馈赠  并予以回礼\NWe accept it in the spirit in which it was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.48,0:51:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你能来\NI'm glad you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.68,0:51:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你的人民和我趵人民可以相互提供很多东西\NI believe your people and mine have much to offer one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.44,0:51:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是外来者  你们来这里是为了香料\NYou are outworlders, you come here for the spice,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.16,0:51:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们拿走香料  却不给任何回报\NYou take it, giving nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.16,0:51:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.24,0:51:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们在哈科宁的手下受了很多苦\NI know you've suffered at the hands of the Harkonnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.86,0:51:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以尽管提要求\NName what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.23,0:51:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是我力所能及的  我会无偿给予\NIf it's in my power to grant I'll give it and ask for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.48,0:52:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我就一要求: 不要再搜寻其他的穴地部落  不要侵入我们的土地\NI ask for this: do not seek our sietches, do not trespass in our lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.00,0:52:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们来这之前  沙漠本是属于我们的\NThe desert was ours long before you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.23,0:52:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你们来了  挖掘香料\NSo, come and dig your spice,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.83,0:52:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等你们挖完香料  又回到屏蔽墙的这一边来\Nbut when you have it, go back to this side of the shield wall
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.43,0:52:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只把一片沙漠留给弗里曼人\Nand leave the desert to the Fremen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.12,0:52:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你要称呼公爵为 "大人" 或 "先生"\NYou will address the Duke as "my lord," or "sir."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.93,0:52:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,格尼  别  不用讲这些\NGurney, just… Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.36,0:52:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝给了我厄拉科斯作为我的领地  我要负责统治和保护\NThe Emperor has given me Arrakis as my fief to rule and protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.08,0:52:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只要上面不要求  我们不会去沙漠乱闯\NI cannot promise not to travel into the desert if duty compels me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.48,0:52:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的穴地部落永远属于你们\NBut your sietches will be yours forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.68,0:52:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在我统治这里期间  你们绝不会遭遇猎杀\Nand you will never be hunted while I govern here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.36,0:52:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是冠冕堂皇啊\NThat's very honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.31,0:52:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\NI must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.32,0:52:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我该说的都说了\NThat's all I have to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.72,0:52:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不留下来呢  我们予你荣誉\NWhy don't you stay. We would honor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.38,0:52:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的荣誉要求我到别的地方去\NHonor requires that I be elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.68,0:52:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁\NI know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.00,0:53:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不喜欢他  -我们的计划会结出硕果\N-I don't like him. -Our plan bears fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.88,0:53:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只是还需要时间\NBut it will take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.20,0:53:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  还需要时间\NYes. It will take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.32,0:53:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给  这是给你的\NHere, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.40,0:53:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个定位罗盘\NIt's a paracompass.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.60,0:53:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的卫星有磁场  所以普通的指南针不会指向北方\NThe moons here have a magnetic field, so a simple compass needle won't point north.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.68,0:53:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,需要这个精密的仪器才行\NTakes a clever piece of clockwork to sort it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.97,0:53:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是弗里曼人做的吗\NDo Fremen make these?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.16,0:53:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还有蒸馏服 沙压器还有各种巧妙的玩意儿\NAnd stillsuits, and sand compactors, and all kinds of ingenious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.80,0:53:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沙压器是什么\NWhat the hell is a sand compactor?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.52,0:53:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沙压器就是沙压器\NThat's a sand compactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.63,0:53:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  伙计  你真像是这土生土长的人\NMy God, man, you've gone native.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.76,0:53:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你很钦佩他们\NYou admire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.08,0:53:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.40,0:53:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很勇猛  也很忠诚\NThey're fierce but loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.52,0:53:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在沙漠里  这些都是一小部分\NThey're tuned into the desert, part of it, it's part of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.37,0:53:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等你有机会到外面见到\NYou wait till you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.52,0:53:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会见到他们的美\NIt's beautiful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.00,0:54:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,日出警报\NSunrise warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.56,0:54:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...气温即将升至140度  现在的温度是90度\N…The temperature up to 140 degrees. The temperature now is 90 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.68,0:54:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,十分钟后将上升50度\NBut it will rise 50 degrees in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.04,0:54:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次警告\NLast warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.28,0:54:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,变时裁决官  先生\NThe Judge of the Change, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.64,0:54:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,列特·凯恩斯博士\NDr. Liet Kynes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.32,0:54:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵大人  欢迎来到厄拉科斯\NMy Lord, Duke, welcome to Arrakis.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.00,0:54:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是帝国生态学家\NYou are the imperial ecologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.91,0:54:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的蒸馏服\NThank you for the stillsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.40,0:54:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是弗里曼人制作的最好的东西\NThey are Fremen make, the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.12,0:55:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您允许  先生  我必须检查一下是否穿戴完整\NWith your permission, sir, I must check the integrity--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.00,0:55:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.40,0:55:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.08,0:55:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,凯恩斯博士  悉听尊便\NDr. Kynes, we're in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.40,0:55:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,蒸馏服是一种很高效的过滤系统\NA stillsuit is a high-efficiency filtration system.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.48,0:55:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是在早晨\NEven this early in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.29,0:55:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没有蒸馏服你也活不了两个小时\Nyou wouldn't survive two hours without one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.64,0:55:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它能使身体降温  并回收因汗而流失的水分\NIt cools the body and recycles the water lost to sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.76,0:55:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且只需身体运动就能提供动能\NYour bodies movements provide the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.80,0:55:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在口罩里面  你会发现一根管子  能让您饮用回收的水分\NInside the mask you'll find a tube to allow you to drink the recycled water.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.40,0:55:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要正常使用  你的蒸馏服一天只会消耗很少一部分水\NIn good-working order your suit won't lose more than a thimble full of water a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.64,0:55:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是厉害\NMost impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.40,0:55:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,让我检查下你的  小伙子\NLet's have a look at you, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-你以前穿过蒸馏服吗  -没有 这是我第一次穿\N-You've worn a stillsuit before? -No, this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.58,0:56:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的沙漠靴子穿在脚上非常贴合  谁教你的\NYour desert boots off at a slip fashion at the ankles. Who taught you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.68,0:56:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉就该这么穿啊\NIt seemed the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.84,0:56:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"此乃正道  与生俱来  你应知道  出神入化"\N"He will know his customs as if he was born with them."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.12,0:56:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是弗里曼人吗\NAre you a Fremen?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.12,0:56:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我被地穴和村庄接纳\NI am accepted in both sietch and village.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.58,0:56:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.56,0:56:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看你们赖以生存的香料沙地吧\NCome and see the spice sands on which your livelihood depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.68,0:57:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的扑翼飞机坠落在这里你会怎么做\NWhat would you do if your ornithopter went down out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.52,0:57:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想去那里的  这是沙虫的领地\NYou wouldn't want to go down out there. It's worm territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.62,0:57:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尘埃云\NDust cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.92,0:57:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了\NI see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.44,0:57:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你们的一辆收割机\NThat's one of your harvesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.12,0:57:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以看到香料散落在表面上\NYou can see the spice scattered over the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.44,0:57:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,形成一个色泽丰富的香料床\NRich spice bed by the color.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.68,0:57:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,飞高一点的话  你会看得更清楚\NIf you get a little higher you'll have a better view.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.44,0:58:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到这些侦察机在寻找沙虫的迹象\NYou see these spotter aircraft looking for worm sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.60,0:58:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么找沙虫的迹象\NWorm sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.08,0:58:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要找向爬行器移动的沙浪就行\NA sand wave moving toward the crawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.31,0:58:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沙虫虽然潜伏的很深  但当它们要发动攻击时会逐渐浮到地面\NWorms travel deep but get closer to the surface when they attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.80,0:58:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们有耐心  我们可以去看看\NIf you are patient we should see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.88,0:58:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-沙虫老是来吗  - 是的 因为它们总是被有节奏的声音所吸引\N-Worm always comes? -Always, they're drawn by rhythmic noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.00,0:58:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们不直接用屏蔽场呢\NWhy don't we just shield the crawlers?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.57,0:58:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠中用屏蔽场就是找死\NA shield is a death sentence in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.92,0:58:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会吸引沙虫  驱使它们疯狂杀戮\NIt attracts the worms and drives them into a killing frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.44,0:58:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是条沙虫吗\NIs that a worm?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.04,0:58:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是个大家伙\NBig one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.70,0:58:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼神真好\NYou have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.06,0:58:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫DA9号  沙虫信号警告  请确认\NCalling crawler Delta Ajax 9. Worm sign warning. Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.72,0:59:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在呼叫DA9号呢  完毕\NWho calls Delta Ajax 9? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.40,0:59:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们似乎对此相当平静  -这里是未登记的帝国业务飞行器\N-They seem pretty calm about it. -Unlisted flight, Imperium business.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.44,0:59:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沙虫位于你的东北方向  三点七公里\NWorm sign, north and east of you. 3.7 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.72,0:59:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,DA9号  这里是侦察机1号  已确认发现沙虫\NDelta Ajax 9, this is Spotter 1, worm sighting confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.16,0:59:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等待修复通讯\NStandby for contact fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.88,0:59:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沙虫正在向你的位置袭来  五分钟后到达\NWorm is on intercept course to your position. Contact in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.88,0:59:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在该怎么做\NSo what happens now?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.96,0:59:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会叫大型运载机去回收香料机车\NThey'll call the carryall to lift the crawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.42,0:59:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会采收到最后一刻\NThey'll harvest right up to the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.52,0:59:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫A0号运载机  准备好停靠\NCalling carryall Alfa Zero. Ready to docking sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.32,0:59:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟后到达  完毕\NContact five minutes, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.32,0:59:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有人看到运载机了吗\NAnybody got a visual on a carryall?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.60,0:59:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是了\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.96,0:59:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是去往DA9号的A0号运载机\NThis is carryall Alfa Zero to Delta Ajax 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.82,0:59:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,从您的东面靠近\NApproaching from your east.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.08,0:59:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,更正高度并准备停靠和抓握\NCorrecting altitude and preparing docking and gripping.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.88,0:59:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  A0号运载机  正在启动停靠序列\NCopy, Alpha Zero. Initiating docking sequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.00,1:00:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-T-5  -收到\N-T-5. -Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.48,1:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-准备在30秒内升空  -停靠序列已启动\N-Prepare to be airborne in 30 seconds. -Docking sequence initiated.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.71,1:00:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,请停靠\NBrace yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.72,1:00:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A0号  有一个支点未连接\NAlpha Zero, we are short on one point of contact.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.32,1:00:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么回事  -是其中一个锚故障了\N-What is going on? -It's one of the anchors. It's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.44,1:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.12,1:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,运载机  无法继续  这锚不连接上无法升空\NCarryall, unable to proceed. Unable to lift without that anchor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.92,1:00:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人员请注意\NAll call. All call.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.80,1:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,此区所有运载机请回复\NAny carryall in the sector, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.72,1:00:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,侦察机1号  请报告最新消息  完毕\NSpotter 1, give us an update. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.64,1:00:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,液压系统故障  我们赶不上了  你们必须撤离\NHydraulics are dead. We won't make it. You have to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.28,1:00:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-那辆机车上有多少人  -21个\N-How many men on that crawler? -Crawler of 21.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.20,1:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们的飞船每艘可以载六个  -还剩三个人\N-Our ships can take six each. -That's still three short.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.76,1:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找到办法的\NWe'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.28,1:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是莱托·厄崔迪公爵\NThis is Duke Leto Atreides.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.84,1:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要下来营救DA9的机组人员\NWe're coming down to extract the crew of Delta Ajax 9.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.10,1:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的侦查机待命行动\NSit down on the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.80,1:01:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,每个屏蔽场发生器重100公斤\NThe shield generators weigh 100 kilos each.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.52,1:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  格尼  让我们的护卫扔掉屏蔽场发生器\NYes, Gurney, have our escort throw out the shield generators.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.36,1:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗  你到推进器后面去  带他们进去\NAnd Paul, I want you at the back of the thopter, guide them in.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.36,1:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,DA9号  往我们的飞船上各派7个人\NDelta Ajax 9, put seven men each in my ships now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.20,1:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沙虫将于两分钟后抵达\NContact in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.08,1:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了  伙计们  我们最好现在赶紧弃船\NIt's getting close, guys. We better abandon the ship now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.60,1:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在哪里\NWhere are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.96,1:02:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我们签了协议的\NSir, there is protocol for a reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.59,1:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们离开这  我们就得死\Nif we take one step out we're as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.10,1:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,另外  我们已经装满了香料  我们不能就这样离开\NBesides, we've got full load of spice, we can't just leave--
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.64,1:02:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的香料  我命令所有人马上从那艘飞船里面出来\NDamn the spice! I want every man off that crawler now!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.00,1:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这边七个  那边七个\NSeven over here, seven over there!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.20,1:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快快快\NRun, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.80,1:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主\NKwisatz Haderach.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.28,1:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主苏醒了\NKwisatz Haderach awakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.48,1:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  上车\NHurry! Get on!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.36,1:03:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沙虫来了\NIt's here!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.92,1:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗\NPaul!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.44,1:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗\NPaul!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.44,1:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我能辨认出你的脚步声  老头\NI recognize your footsteps, old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.24,1:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快起来  我们走吧\NGet up. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.56,1:04:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了  快点  赶紧跑\NWhat's wrong with you? Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.80,1:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,跑啊\NRun!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.88,1:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,赞美造物主与他的水  赞美他翻来覆去\N"Bless the Maker and His water. Bless the coming and going of Him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.44,1:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,愿他所到之处  净化大地  为民护地\NMay His passage cleanse the world. And keep the world for His people."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.40,1:05:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-嘿 你不能冒这样的风险  -是的 先生\N-Hey, you cannot take such risks. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.64,1:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-你身负重任  -对不起 先生 这种事不会再发生了\N-You do have responsibilities. -I'm sorry, sir. It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.96,1:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,凯恩斯博士\NDr. Kynes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.00,1:05:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你亲眼看到了吧\NYou saw it with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.96,1:05:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显  他们留给我们的都是些残次品\NIt's plain to see. Everything they've left us is in shambles.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.65,1:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这样肯定会失败的\NWe've been set up to fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.96,1:05:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那辆车只是太旧了  沙漠对设备损坏程度很高\NThat carryall was just old. The desert isn't kind to equipment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.16,1:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道如果我不能让香料生产重回正轨  会有什么后果吗\NYou know what will happen if I don't get spice production back on track?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.36,1:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是来跟你换位思考的\NI'm not here to take your part.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.12,1:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,厄拉科斯有很多像你这样的人来来去去\NArrakis has seen men like you come and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.56,1:06:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好好照顾你的家人吧\NTake good care of your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.04,1:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠对人类也很不友好\NThe desert's not kind to humans either.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.12,1:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,香料是一种具有精神活性的化学物质  看来你很敏感\NSpice is a psychoactive chemical. You seem to be sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.20,1:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的\NYou'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.44,1:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  岳医生\NThank you, Dr. Yueh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.56,1:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是过敏反应\NIt wasn't an allergic reaction.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.96,1:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时看到了一个场景\NI had a vision.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.98,1:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛睁得大大的\NMy eyes were wide open.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.60,1:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么\NWhat did you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.12,1:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主\NKwisatz Haderach…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.92,1:07:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,您可以看到\NYou can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.77,1:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚  我以为我看到了我之死  但并非如此\NIt's confusing, I thought I saw my death, only it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.44,1:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么  好像有一把刀很重要\NI know a knife is important somehow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.64,1:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有人会给我一把刀\NSomeone will hand me a blade.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.24,1:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道谁会给我  也不知道什么时候会在哪给我\NBut I don't know who or when or where.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.80,1:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但我又感觉  冥冥之中一切已注定\NSome things though are crystal clear. I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.52,1:09:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你怀孕了\NI know you're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.60,1:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能知道的\NYou can't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.84,1:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是刚知道  而且才过了几个星期\NI barely know that and it's only been few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.32,1:09:30.80,Default,tag,0,0,0,,萨卢萨·塞孔杜斯\N\N帝国军队星球
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.48,1:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,男爵要我们做什么\NWhat does the Baron want with us?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.68,1:10:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁的人比厄崔迪人多\NThe Harkonnen outnumber Atreides.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.84,1:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,厄崔迪的军团是帝国中最优秀的\NAtreides legions are the finest in the Imperium.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.32,1:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是由格尼·哈莱克和邓肯·爱达荷精心训练的\NTrained by Gurney Halleck and Duncan Idaho.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.08,1:10:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是萨督卡帝国军团  任何违抗我们的人都将倒下\NWe are the Sardaukar, the Emperor's elite. Anyone who defies us will fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.04,1:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正是如此\NJust so.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.32,1:10:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,按照旨意  要三个营的人\NThree battalions as agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.12,1:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是皇帝的旨意  定当完成\NAs the the Emperor commands. It will be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.72,1:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有些关于保罗的事你必须知道\NThere's something you need to know about Paul.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.16,1:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我觉得我不想知道\NNo. I don't think I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.96,1:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,自从你把他带到你尊敬的圣母那去之后\NEver since you brought him before your Reverend Mother
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.28,1:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他变了\Nhe hasn't been the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.48,1:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他心烦意乱\NHe's distracted.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.64,1:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杰西卡  你给我生了个儿子\NJessica, you gave me a son.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.92,1:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,从他出生的那一刻起我就没有质疑过你\NAnd from the moment he was born I never questioned you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.16,1:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全信任你  即使你暗度陈仓\NI trusted you completely, even when you walked in shadows.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.68,1:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只问你一件事\NNow I'm asking you this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.04,1:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果发生什么事  你会保护我们的儿子吗\NIf anything happens will you protect our son?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.32,1:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用我的性命保护他\NWith my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.64,1:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在问你  我是在问贝内·格塞里特家族\NI'm not asking his mother, I'm asking the Bene Gesserit.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.28,1:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会保护保罗吗\NWill you protect Paul?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.48,1:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么会有这些想法\NWhy are you having these thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.52,1:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,莱托  你以前可不这样\NLeto, this is not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.44,1:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我们会有更多时间\NI thought we'd have more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.92,1:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚安 保罗少爷  -晚安 岳医生\N-Have a good night, Master Paul. -Good night, Dr. Yueh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.52,1:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要休息一下\NYou need to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.24,1:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不要那个\NNo, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.68,1:13:13.56,Default,tag,0,0,35,,保罗母亲是其父亲的爱妾
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.68,1:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我真该娶你为妻的\NI should have married you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.92,1:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瓦特  安保\NHawat. Security.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.84,1:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,安保\NSecurity!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.56,1:15:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  先生\NSir. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.00,1:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,屏蔽场被关闭了\NThe shield's come down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.28,1:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\NGod in Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.20,1:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所有带炮的飞行器全部升空  快\NGet everything with guns off the ground! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.40,1:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\NWith me!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.16,1:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,厄崔迪\NAtreides!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.48,1:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,萨督卡\NSardaukar!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.48,1:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  大人\NI'm sorry, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.92,1:19:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已经和男爵达成了协议\NBut I've made a bargain with the Baron.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.04,1:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么  -我别无选择\N-Why? -I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.24,1:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁人抓走了我的妻子  万娜\NThe Harkonners have my wife, Wanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.89,1:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要把她像洋娃娃一样肢解\NThey take her apart like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.32,1:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我得救她  而你就是他们开的条件\NI will buy her freedom and you are the price.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.80,1:19:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽可能把这交给保罗\NFor Paul. I will do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.68,1:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你得为我杀一个人\NAnd you will kill a man for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.52,1:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你换颗钉牙\NI'm going to replace your peg tooth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.00,1:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你用力一咬  这颗牙就会碎掉\NIf you bite them hard, this tooth will crash.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.84,1:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要吐一口气  空气中就会充满毒气\NBreathe out, and you will fill the air with poison.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.84,1:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是你最后一口气\NIt will be your last breath.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.69,1:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要你选对了时机\NBut if you choose your moment well
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.52,1:19:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以拉男爵陪葬\Nit will also be the Baron's.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.16,1:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗\NPaul.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.44,1:21:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把他们丢进沙漠里  任由沙虫吞食\NWe will drop them in the desert, and leave them to the worms.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.40,1:21:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不直接割断他们的喉咙呢\NWhy not just cut their throats?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.00,1:21:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们答应了女先知\NThey might use a Truthsayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.16,1:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把他们扔进沙漠  就不是我们杀死的他们了\NThen we can honestly say that we didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.72,1:22:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有伤疤的那个是聋子\NThe one with the scar is deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.52,1:22:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼去吧  狗杂种\NTo hell, dogs!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.04,1:24:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我没操过贵族呢\NI've never had a high-born.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.88,1:24:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你呢  -贝内·格瑟里特家族的也不全是贵族\N-You? -Bene Gesserit ain't no high-born.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.28,1:24:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她出生高贵  我配不上她\NShe is high-born enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.24,1:24:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把这孩子喂给沙虫吃  让他们母子诀别\NLet's feed the kid to the worms and give her a long goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.32,1:24:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不准碰我妈妈\NDon't you dare touch my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.16,1:24:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别说话\NDon't talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.76,1:24:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱来  你还没准备好\NNo. You're not ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.16,1:24:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把她嘴上的布取下来\NRemove her gag.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.44,1:25:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\NShut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.36,1:25:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,注意密语的音调\NFind the right tone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.28,1:25:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了  我们把那个男孩扔下去吧\NWe're far enough. Let's throw the boy off.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.72,1:25:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把她嘴上的布拿开\NRemove her gag.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.28,1:25:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了他\NKill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.64,1:25:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还我们自由\NSet us free.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.68,1:26:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,停  把绳子剪断\NStop. Cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.16,1:26:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把刀给我\NGive me the knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.04,1:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你用密语有点用力过猛了\NYour pitch was too forced.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.71,1:26:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是弗里曼人的工具包\NIt's a Fremkit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.16,1:26:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把船弄坏了\NThey've crippled the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.24,1:28:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的厨房真不错  表弟\NYou have a wonderful kitchen, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.59,1:28:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是岳医生的笔迹\NThis is Dr. Yueh's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.46,1:28:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"如果有人活着离开了厄拉科斯  工具包里有厄崔迪的信标\N"If anyone makes it out of Arrakeen alive there's an Atreides beacon in the Fremkit.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.22,1:28:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑他们能找到你"\NGod willing they'd be able to find you."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.80,1:28:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,伯爵大人  这是岳医生\NMilord Baron, Dr. Yueh.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.28,1:28:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叛徒?\NThe traitor?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.04,1:29:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.28,1:29:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我干扰了他们的通讯并关闭了他们的屏蔽场\NI jammed their comms and lowered their shields.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.86,1:29:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把公爵和他的家人都交给了你\NI gave you Duke and his family.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.12,1:29:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谈条件就爽快点  需要我做什么\NThe bargain to the letter. And what was I to do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.96,1:29:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把我妻子从痛苦中解救出来\NDeliver my wife from her agony.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.36,1:29:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.80,1:29:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我会放了她  你才能跟她团聚\NI said I'd set her free, that you could join her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.24,1:30:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就跟她团聚吧\NSo join her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.72,1:30:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得接下来该怎么做呢\NWhat do you think is next?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.24,1:30:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是个沙槌\NIt's a thumper.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.58,1:30:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没有蒸馏服\NNo stillsuits.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.50,1:30:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,蒸馏服才是我们最需要的\NThe one thing we actually need.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.88,1:30:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,几百年来  我们血债血偿\NFor hundreds of years we've traded blood for blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.33,1:30:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但以后不会再有了\NBut no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.48,1:30:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,尔儿子死了  你的爱妾死了\NYour son is dead. Your concubine is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.56,1:30:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚厄崔迪家族陨落...\NTonight the house Atreides falls…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.76,1:30:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你的血统就会永远终结\Nand your bloodline ends forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.72,1:31:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,您说什么\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.20,1:31:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"我在这里  我还在这里"\N"Here I am, here I remain!"
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.32,1:32:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-凯恩斯  -你不该来这\N-Kynes! -It's not safe for you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.88,1:33:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你能说说帝国和兰斯拉德的各大家族是怎么背叛我们的吗\NWill you tell the Great House of the Landsraad how we were betrayed?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.99,1:33:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为何要这般谋杀\NHow the best of them were murdered?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.32,1:33:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我奉命闭口不谈  视若不见\NI am commanded to say nothing, to see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.96,1:33:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝把我们送到这里是来送死的\NThe Emperor sent us here to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.76,1:34:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,罐子里有香料\NSpice in the tank.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.36,1:35:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是未来  就要来了\NThat's the future. It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.82,1:35:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,圣战正像一团无法熄灭的大火一样席卷整个宇宙\NThe Holy war is spreading across the universe like an unquenchable fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.64,1:36:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗  你很害怕  我看得出来  请告诉我  你在害怕什么\NPaul, you're scared. I can see it. Tell me, please, what do you fear?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.20,1:36:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁来帮帮我 拜托  -保罗...\N-Somebody help me, please. -Paul…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.39,1:36:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要来了\NIt's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.38,1:36:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,圣战正像一团无法熄灭的大火一样席卷整个宇宙\NThe Holy war is spreading across the universe like an unquenchable fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.36,1:36:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一好战宗教  高举厄崔迪的战旗\NA warrior religion that waves the Atreides banner in my father's name.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.49,1:36:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,狂战军团  在我父亲遗骸的圣殿中膜拜\NFanatical legions worshiping at the shine of my father's skull.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.20,1:36:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以我的名义  每个人都高呼我的名字\NA war in my name! Everyone shouting my name!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.40,1:36:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗\NPaul.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.04,1:36:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗·厄崔迪...\NPaul Atreides…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.08,1:36:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是你父亲的儿子  也是我的儿子\NYou are your father's son. You are my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.22,1:36:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是保罗·厄崔迪公爵\NYou are Duke Paul Atreides.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.68,1:36:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你是谁\NYou know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.44,1:36:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我\NGet off me!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.24,1:36:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是你把我弄成这样的  你的贝内·格塞里特让我成了怪胎\NYou did this to me! Your Bene Gesserit made me a freak!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.52,1:37:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸死了\NMy dad is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.68,1:38:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在附近\NSomeone is near.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.13,1:38:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要喝点水\NYou need to drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.80,1:38:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是帐篷里的循环水\NIt's recycled water from the tent.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.60,1:38:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,回收的汗水和泪水\NSweat and tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.92,1:38:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  快离开这\NAll right. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.08,1:39:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是邓肯\NIt's Duncan.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.00,1:39:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人  保罗...\NMy Lady. Paul…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.44,1:39:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-我很抱歉 你父亲...  -我们知道\N-I'm so sorry… Your father… -We know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.84,1:39:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵大人\NMy Lord Duke.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.46,1:40:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.55,1:40:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个喝了\NDrink this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.11,1:40:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈科宁人一下子袭击了我们星球上所有的人口聚集地\NThe Harkonnens hit every population center on the planet at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.44,1:40:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,起码有十个军团  上百艘战船\NIt must've been ten legions, hundreds of ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.99,1:40:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,萨督卡和他们在一起\NThere were Sardaukar with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.56,1:40:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-至少有两个营  -你确定吗\N-At least two battalions. -Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.52,1:40:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我和萨督卡交过手  你知道的\NYou cross swords with the Sardaukar, you know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.24,1:40:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  皇帝已经站队了\NSo, the Emperor's taken a side.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.18,1:40:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,变时裁决官有什么要说的吗\NWhat says the Judge of the Change?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.10,1:40:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝根本不给我发言权\NThe Emperor forbids me from saying anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.32,1:40:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你冒着生命危险来帮助我们\NYet you risk your life to help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.72,1:41:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沙暴就要来了\NThe storm is coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.00,1:41:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沙暴几个小时后就到了  我们在这里会比较安全\NThe storm will be here in a few hours. We'll be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.68,1:41:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么地方吗  这是一个古老的生态试验站\NDo you know what this place is? It's an old ecological testing station.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.48,1:41:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们本来是要控制这个星球\NThe were meant to tame the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.37,1:41:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把藏在沙子下的水找出来\Nand free the water locked beneath the sands.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.54,1:41:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,厄拉科斯本可以成为天堂\NArrakis could have been a paradise.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.04,1:41:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,工作开始后  他们发现了香料\NThe work had begun but then the spice was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.06,1:41:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一时间  他们都不希望消除沙漠了\Nand suddenly no one wanted the desert to go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.84,1:41:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,塔纳特  你能找一套适合我们的蒸馏服吗\NTanat, will you find stillsuits to fit our visitors.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.71,1:41:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  列特\NYes, Liet.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.79,1:41:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-沙米尔 来几杯咖啡  -好的 列特\N-Shamir, coffee service, please. -Of course, Liet.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.94,1:41:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是弗里曼人的什么人\NWho are you to the Fremen?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.68,1:42:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道大家族最害怕什么吗  凯恩斯博士\NDo you know what the great houses fear most, Dr. Kynes?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.32,1:42:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这儿所发生的一切\NExactly what has happened to us here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.12,1:42:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,萨督卡来了  一个接一个地把他们干掉\NThe Sardaukar coming and picking them off one by one.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.88,1:43:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只有齐心协力  才有机会对抗帝国\NOnly together can they stand a chance against the Imperium.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.12,1:43:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意作证吗\NWould you bare witness?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.30,1:43:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,证明皇帝在这里对我们采取了行动\NTestify that the Emperor has moved against us here.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.28,1:43:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们相信我的话...\NIf they believe me…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.32,1:43:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大家族们和皇帝之间将会开启一场全面的战争\NThere would be general warfare between the great houses and the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.88,1:43:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,整个帝国都会混乱\NChaos across the Imperium.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.96,1:43:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我给皇帝一个混乱之外的选择呢\NLet's suppose I present to the Emperor with an alternative to chaos.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.16,1:43:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝没有儿子  他的女儿们还没有结婚\NAnd the Emperor has no sons, and his daughters are yet to marry.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.72,1:43:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你要在皇帝面前玩把戏吗\NYou'd make a play for the throne?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.83,1:43:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝畏惧厄崔迪家族  他把你们带到这里来是为了杀你们\NThe Emperor feared the Atreides. He brought you here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.20,1:43:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不明白吗\NWhat don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.68,1:43:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个无家可归的孩子  躲在地穴里\NYou're a lost boy hiding in a hole in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.96,1:43:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里曼人称我为救世主\NThe Fremen speak of the Lisan al-Gaib.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.08,1:43:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\NCareful.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.80,1:43:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能将他们带到天堂的异域先知\NThe Voice from the Outer World who will lead them to paradise.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.76,1:43:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都是迷信\NSuperstition.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.52,1:44:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你爱过一个弗里曼战士  却在战争中失去了他\NI know you loved a Fremen warrior and lost him in battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.56,1:44:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你生活在两个世界  有很多人都知道你的名字\NI know you walk in two worlds and are known by many names.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.84,1:44:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的梦想\NI've seen your dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.93,1:44:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要是当了皇帝  凯恩斯博士\NAs Emperor, Dr. Kynes,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.45,1:44:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只要挥挥手  我就能为厄拉科斯打造一个天堂\NI could make a paradise for Arrakis with the wave of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.88,1:44:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的认为他会是救世主吗\NDo you really think he could be the Mahdi?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.84,1:44:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起来很年轻\NHe looks very young.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.64,1:46:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,萨督卡\NSardaukar!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.64,1:46:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 邓肯  -保罗 不\N-No! Duncan! -Paul, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.04,1:46:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-邓肯 不  -他锁上门了\N-Duncan, no! -He's locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.84,1:47:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\NHe's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.47,1:47:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,邓肯\NDuncan!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.48,1:47:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我偏得走了  我们别无选择\NWe have to go. We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.48,1:47:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗  快跑\NPaul, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.92,1:47:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快点\NCome on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.12,1:48:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着光走  你会发现一台沙漠版的扑翼飞机\NFollow the light. You'll find a thopter ready to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.61,1:48:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的沙暴是你最好的逃离的机会\NThat storm out there is your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.40,1:48:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沙暴足足有5000米高  大部分是沙尘  飞进去后  留在沙暴上方\NAbove 5000 meters, it's mostly dust. Climb into it. Stay on top.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.11,1:48:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-沙暴结束后 向南走 能找到弗里曼人  -你不和我们一起去吗\N-Head south. Find the Fremen. -You're not coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.10,1:48:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机只有两个座位\NIt only sits two.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.37,1:48:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我去下一站  向兰斯拉德各大家族报告这次袭击\NI'll go to the next station and report this attack to the Landsraad.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.92,1:48:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么去\NHow?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.84,1:48:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是弗里曼人  沙漠是我的家\NI'm Fremen. The desert is my home.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.32,1:48:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝你们好运  -祝你好运\N-Good luck. -Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.00,1:51:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,凯恩斯  你背叛了皇帝\NKynes, you have betrayed the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.76,1:51:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我只服侍一位主人\NI serve only one master.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.33,1:51:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是  沙虫\NHis name is Shai-Hulud.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.84,1:52:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们身局有喷气式飞机\NThere are jet flyers behind us.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.60,1:52:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗  我们不够高\NPaul, we are not high enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.72,1:53:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能 害怕  恐惧是心灵杀手\NI must not fear. Fear is the mind-killer.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.00,1:53:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,恐惧只会带来毁灭\NFear is the little-death that brings total obliteration.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.80,1:53:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊  朋友\NSee the friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.76,1:53:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,生命的谜团并不是需要解决的问题\NThe mystery of life isn't a problem to solve.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.80,1:53:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现实的体验才是\NBut a reality to experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.84,1:53:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个无法暂停来理解的过程\NA process that cannot be understand by stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.32,1:53:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须跟随其前行\NWe must move with the flow of the process.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.68,1:54:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须加入  随其前行\NWe must join it. We must float with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.08,1:54:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他还没有完全痊愈\NHe hasn't fully healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.36,1:54:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们追赶他们进入了科里奥利风暴\NWe chased them into a Coriolis storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.64,1:55:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,风速是每小时800公里\NWind's at 800 kilometers an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.20,1:55:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能在这样的风暴中幸存下来\NNothing survives such a storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.92,1:55:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必死无疑\NThey're dead. It's a certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.20,1:55:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以终于结束了\NSo it's done finally.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.18,1:55:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,传话给吉迪主星  开始出售我们储备的香料\NSend word to Giedi Prime to begin selling our spice reserves.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.64,1:55:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不过慢点卖  我们不希望价格下跌\NBut slowly. We don't want the price to fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.48,1:55:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我把这样一支军队带过去花了多少钱\NYou have no idea how much it cost me to bring such a force to barrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.52,1:55:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只有一个要求  赚钱\NNow I only have one requirement. Income.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.12,1:55:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  压榨  拉班  使劲压榨\NSo, squeeze, Rabban. Squeeze hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.00,1:55:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  叔叔\NYes, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.94,1:55:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里曼人怎么处理\NAnd the Fremen?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.00,1:55:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们都杀了\NKill them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.88,1:56:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在5000米以上\NWe're above 5000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.40,1:57:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦着陆  就会击毁在岩石上\NAs soon as we land, run for the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.52,1:59:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个呼吸\NYou breathe with this.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.44,2:00:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们必须找到弗里曼人\NNow we have to find the Fremen.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.04,2:00:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-你还好吗  -是的\N-Are you good? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.84,2:01:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗\NPaul…
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.80,2:01:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕\NDon't be frightened.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.72,2:01:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是一只小小的沙漠老鼠也能存活\NEven a little desert mouse can survive.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.88,2:01:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要面对你的恐惧\NYou'll need to face your fears.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.04,2:01:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友会帮助你的\NA friend will help you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.48,2:01:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,跟随你的朋友\NFollow the friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.36,2:01:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有很多东西要学\NYou have much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.36,2:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我会指引你沙漠里的道路\NAnd I will show you the ways of the desert.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.12,2:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来吧\NCome with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.24,2:02:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,穴地  邓肯曾经住过\NThe sietch, where Duncan lived.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.76,2:02:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这的某个地方\NSomewhere off that way.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.30,2:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看到那边的绿色\NI can see the green over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.00,2:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那里\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.08,2:02:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着弗里曼人住在那\NThat means Fremen live there.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.28,2:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得在天黑后过河  弗里曼人就是这么做的\NWe'll cross after dark. That's how the Fremen do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.24,2:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们即将进入沙虫领域\NWe're about to enter worm territory.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.91,2:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝不能像普通人那样走路  否则我们就死定了\NWe can't walk like regular humans, if we do - we're dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.72,2:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得像弗里曼人那样走路  这叫沙子漫步\NWe'll have to walk like the Fremen do. It's called the sand walk.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.32,2:03:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至少从国内的电影和书上是这样说的\NAt least according to the film books back home.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.33,2:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  好的  我明白\NYeah. Yeah, I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.60,2:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  跟我来  做同样的动作\NOkay, follow me. Do the same moves.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.38,2:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为是这个方向\NI think this is the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.88,2:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就在附近  我们赶紧走\NIt's close by. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.84,2:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.60,2:04:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是沙鼓\NIt's drum sand.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.32,2:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,跑\NRun!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.12,2:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快  快\NGo! Go!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.52,2:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是沙槌的声音\NIt's a thumper.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.44,2:06:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在敲沙槌\NSomeone set off a thumper.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.16,2:06:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗  快跑\NPaul, run!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.36,2:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它们也太大了吧  太疯狂了\NHow big are they? That was insane.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.40,2:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把它引走了\NSomeone called him.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.64,2:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并不孤单\NWe are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.24,2:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别跑了\NDo not run.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.52,2:07:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只会浪费你们的身体内的水\NYou will only waste your bodies water.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.12,2:07:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\NHold.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:48.20,2:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂加\NStilgar.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.00,2:07:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你认识我的  当你来见我父亲时  我就在那里\NHey, you know me. I was there when you came to my father's council.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.52,2:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是公爵的儿子\NThis is the Duke's son.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.68,2:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在等什么呢  我们需要他们的水\NWhy are you waiting? We need their water.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.28,2:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我跟你们说过的那个男孩  我们不能碰他\NThis is the boy I told you about. We can't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.76,2:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是救世主吗  -他还没有证明自己\N-Is he Lisan al-Gaib? -He hasn't proved himself.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.88,2:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们是弱者  -杰米斯\N-They're weaklings. -Jamis…
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.44,2:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在沙虫的地盘上勇敢地穿梭而来\NThere was a brave crossing they made in the path of Shai-Hulud.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.72,2:08:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他说话和行为都不像个懦夫\NHe does not speak or act like a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.71,2:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的父亲也不是需夫\NNor did his father.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.54,2:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的沙槌救了他的命\NMy thumper saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.12,2:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,理性点  史蒂加  他不是救世主\NGo back to reason, Stilgar. He's not The One.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.72,2:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多有权势的朋友\NWe have powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.60,2:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们帮我们离开这个星球  去卡拉丹  一定能给你们不少回报\NYou help us off world, to Caladan, you will be well rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.92,2:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,除了你身体里的水  你还能提供什么回报呢\NWhat wealth can you offer beyond the water in your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:45.88,2:08:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男孩很小  他可以接受我们的训练\NThe boy is young. He can learn our ways.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.69,2:08:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以得到庇护\NHe may have sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.40,2:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个女人没有受过训练\NBut the woman isn't trained
Dialogue: 0,2:08:57.11,2:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且年纪太大了  学不会了\Nand too old to learn.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.48,2:09:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,后退  你们这些蠢货\NBack, you dogs!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.17,2:09:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她会割断我的喉咙\NShe'll cut my throat.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.92,2:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何不说你是练过玄秘之道的女战士\NWhy didn't you say you were a weirding woman and a fighter?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.04,2:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们根本也没聊几句啊\NThe conversation ran short.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.40,2:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静  女人  冷静\NPeace, woman, peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.65,2:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的错\NI misjudged.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.00,2:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳快升起了  我们必须到达山脊洞穴\NThe sun is rising. We must reach Sietch Tabr.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.24,2:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,外人之命  去了那再做决断\NThe fate of the strangers will be decided there.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.80,2:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前  我保他们性命\NUntil then, they are under my protection.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.92,2:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你们保证\NI give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.84,2:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你伤害我的朋友\NI would not have let you hurt my friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.20,2:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说你是救世主\NThey say you are the Mahdi.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.51,2:10:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但你看起来不过是个小男孩\NBut you look like a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.96,2:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你选择了最艰难的上山之路  跟我来吧\NYou chose the hardest way up. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.96,2:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧走了\NTake off! Take off!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.76,2:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把它给我\NGive it to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.12,2:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当你证明了自己的身份  会把枪给你的\NYou would have your own maula pistol when you've earned it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.33,2:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,把它给我\NGive it to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.84,2:11:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,查尼  你负责新来的人  注意他们在旅途中的安全\NChani, take charge of the newcomers. See that they are safe in the journey.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:33.05,2:11:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.28,2:11:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意他们一起走\NI will not have them.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.88,2:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,贾米斯  我已经说过了  别乱来\NJamis, I have spoken. Be still.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.76,2:11:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你虽说是个领袖  但没有最强的实力\NYou talk like a leader, but the strongest leads.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.20,2:11:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她打败了你\NShe bested you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.84,2:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要发起挑战\NI invoke the Amtal.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.72,2:12:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不能挑战圣母  -那谁能挑战\N-You may not challenge a sayyadina. -Then who will fight in her name?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.24,2:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,贾米斯  别乱来了  夜色将尽\NJamis, don't do this. Don't. The night is fading.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.40,2:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那不妨让太阳来见证这场死亡\NThen the sun will witness this death.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.28,2:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她的捍卫者呢\NWhere is her champion?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.56,2:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受她的捍卫者\NI accept her champion.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.98,2:12:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗·厄崔迪必须死...\NPaul Atreides must die…
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.88,2:13:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主才能得以崛起\Nfor Kwisatz Haderach to rise.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:05.92,2:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕  不要抗拒\NDon't be frightened. Don't resist.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.88,2:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当你要取走一条性命时  你得取走自己的生命\NWhen you take a life, you take your own.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.96,2:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信你是救世主\NI don't believe you are the Lisan al-Gaib.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.72,2:13:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但我希望你死得光荣\NBut I want you to die with honor.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.76,2:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这把晶牙匕是我外婆给我的\NThis crysknife was given to me by my great-aunt.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.56,2:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是由一只巨大的沙虫的一颗牙齿制成的\NIt's made from a tooth of Shai-Hulud, the great sand worm.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.72,2:14:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你以此匕战败  也是莫大的荣誉\NThis would be a great honor if you to die holding it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.60,2:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,外来者在哪里\NWhere is the outworlder?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.28,2:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,贾米斯是个很厉害的战士  他会很决绝的\NJamis is a good fighter. He won't let you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.00,2:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,查尼...\NChani…
Dialogue: 0,2:14:52.32,2:14:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别介意\NNever mind.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.72,2:15:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你刀断人亡\NMay your knife chip and shatter.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:56.24,2:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要迎接我的刀锋\NYou should welcome my blade.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:01.48,2:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界迟早会干掉你\NThis world will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:06.36,2:16:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮你早点解脱\NQuicker this way.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:45.92,2:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你要投降吗\NDo you yield?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.72,2:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男孩不知道我们的规则\NThe boy does not know our rule.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:52.03,2:16:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的规则没有投降  只有死亡\NThere is no yielding under the Amtal rule, only death is the test of that.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.00,2:17:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是在耍他吗  -不\N-Is he toying with him? -No.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:07.12,2:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗从未杀过人\NPaul has never killed a man.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.32,2:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主\NKwisatz Haderach.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:26.16,2:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主\NKwisatz Haderach.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.20,2:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,爬上去  崛起吧\NClimb up. Rise.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.92,2:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是我们中的一员了  一命换一命\NYou're one of us now. A life for a life.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:24.64,2:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-和我们一起去山脊洞穴吧  -不\N-Come with us to Sietch Tabr. -No.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.60,2:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗需要离开这个星球\NPaul needs to get off world.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:29.18,2:19:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定有办法的  你有走私的人  你有飞船\NYou must have ways. You have smugglers, you have ships.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.21,2:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  -你有\N-No. -You have--
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.65,2:19:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,皇帝把我们送到这个地方\NThe Emperor sent us to this place.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:37.96,2:19:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲来了...\NAnd my father came…
Dialogue: 0,2:19:40.60,2:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是为了香料  也不是为了财富\NNot for spice, not for the riches,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:45.16,2:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而是为了团结你们人民的力量\Nbut for the strength of your people.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:50.08,2:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的前途通向沙漠\NMy road leads into the desert.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:54.56,2:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得出来\NI could see it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.32,2:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意接待我们  我们就会随你们去\NIf you'll have us, we will come.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.16,2:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠力量\NDesert power.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.68,2:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是个开始\NThis is only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:53.18,2:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,


